/** @page index Libgsqlw

This is a documentation for @b libgsqlw: glib sql wrapper.
Libgsqlw is a wrapper for different databases. Currently supports PostgreSQL, SQLite and MySQL.

@section howto HOWTO

To start using gsqlw first function you must call is @ref gs_connect(const char *dsn) 
where dsn format varies depending on desired database engine.
@li PostgreSQL - "pgsql:dbname=test host=localhost user=postgres password=pass"
@li SQLite - "sqlite:.test.db"
@li MySQL - "mysql:servername;username;password;dbname;2048", last parameter is max length of string values in database


